<define-tag pagetitle>Debian GNU/Linux 2.2r3 released</define-tag>
<define-tag release_date>2001-04-17</define-tag>
#use wml::debian::news

<p>The third revision of Debian GNU/Linux 2.2 (nickname `potato') has
been released. This point release, version 2.2r3, mostly includes
security updates, along with a few corrections to important bugs in
the stable distribution.

<p>Upgrading to this revision online can be done by pointing the `apt'
package tool (see sources.list(5) manual page) to one of Debian's many
FTP mirrors.  A list is available at:

<div class="center">
  <a href="$(HOME)/distrib/ftplist">https://www.debian.org/distrib/ftplist</a>
</div>

